This project requires CMake to build.
http://cmake.org


BUILDING FFMPEG-FAS

LINUX:
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..


WINDOWS: (using cmake gui)
build dir: fas-root/build
source dir: fas-root
where fas-root is this folder.


WINDOWS (using command prompt):
md build
cd build
cmake ..

To generate MSVC project files, you can use cmake-gui and select your version of MSVC, or use cmake .. -G <generator>.
Use cmake --help to determine the correct generator.



Tests are not part of this cmake system yet, but will be soon.
